.TH stat 1  "stat " 
.SH NAME
stat \- Show detailed metadata for a local file
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstat\fR [\fB\-\-terse\fR] [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-threads\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPATH\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show detailed metadata for a local file
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-terse\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-threads\fR \fI<THREADS>\fR [default: 0]
Scanner threads (1 disables parallelism, 0 uses all available CPUs)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPATH\fR>

